LOCUS       Twin_Strep_tag            30 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Twin-Strep-tag: two tandem Strep-tag II (WSHPQFEK) units joined by a
            GGGSGGGSGGS linker, conferring bivalent high-avidity binding to
            Strep-Tactin/Strep-Tactin XT for one-step affinity purification and
            detection..
