                     /synonym="Twin Strep tag"
                     /note="Tandem affinity tag: two Strep-tag II (WSHPQFEK)
                     units connected by a GGGSGGGSGGS flexible linker, with an
                     N-terminal Ser-Ala. Bivalency lowers the off-rate from
                     Strep-Tactin/Strep-Tactin XT, giving picomolar-range
                     avidity and enabling near-irreversible capture with mild
                     competitive (biotin/desthiobiotin) elution. Sequence
                     confirmed 100% over 30 aa against PDB 6SOS chain R."
